    <h3  class="f4-mktg color-fg-muted pb-2" aria-hidden="true"> Nubank</h3>
    <p  class="h6-mktg color-fg-default py-1 pb-sm-4 text-semibold" aria-hidden="true">By prioritizing collaboration through open source practices, Nubank centers its DevOps on GitHub so they can focus on customers.</p>
